Reading in data
=================

Data exists in various forms

-  Text files
  -  (Comma) delimited (csv)
  -  Tabular (fixed format) text (tab)
-  Excel spreadsheets
-  Databases
  -  Local (MS Access, SQLite)
  -  Server (Oracle, IBM DB2, MySQL)
-  Web API
  - Twitter, Facebook, Google, Quandl
  
